OL,3,CShould North Somerset join the
OL,4,Ccombined authority? Consultation gets
OL,5,Cunderway
OL,7,FA public consultation on North
OL,8,FSomerset Council joining the West of
OL,9,FEngland Mayoral Combined Authority
OL,10,Fopens today (Friday 13 February).
OL,12,FBusinesses and residents across Bath &
OL,13,FNorth East Somerset, Bristol, North
OL,14,FSomerset, and South Gloucestershire
OL,15,Fare being invited to have their say on
OL,16,Fthe proposals until 10 April.
OL,18,FBosses say if it goes ahead, the West
OL,19,Fcould receive millions more in funding
OL,20,Ffor projects, including housing and
OL,21,Ftransport.
