OL,3,CShould North Somerset join the
OL,4,Ccombined authority? Consultation gets
OL,5,Cunderway
OL,7,FIf North Somerset were to join WECA,
OL,8,Fthe population of the combined
OL,9,Fauthority would increase by 23%, to a
OL,10,Ftotal of 1.225 million people.
OL,12,FThe would mean the Government would
OL,13,Fallocate a larger pot of devolved
OL,14,Ffunding to the region, after the
OL,15,Fgovernment previously committed that,
OL,16,Fshould the expansion proceed, future
OL,17,Ffunding would "take account of an
OL,18,Fexpanded WECA geography and
OL,19,Fpopulation."
