OL,3,CShould North Somerset join the
OL,4,Ccombined authority? Consultation gets
OL,5,Cunderway
OL,7,FWECA said after negotiations with
OL,8,Fnational government, an additional #15
OL,9,Fmillion has been allocated for
OL,10,Fprojects in the region in the short-
OL,11,Fterm, should North Somerset join. An
OL,12,Fadditional #1 million has been offered
OL,13,Fto assist with the process of the
OL,14,Flocal authority joining Bath & North
OL,15,FEast Somerset, Bristol, and South
OL,16,FGloucestershire councils as a full
OL,17,Fmember of the regional authority.
OL,19,FIt's thought increased funding would
OL,20,Fbe put towards transport improvements
OL,21,Fand housing projects.
