OL,3,CShould North Somerset join the
OL,4,Ccombined authority? Consultation gets
OL,5,Cunderway
OL,7,FThe authority, added the West, has the
OL,8,Fstrongest recent economic growth of
OL,9,Fany region in the country and, since
OL,10,F2019, has consistently grown at four
OL,11,Ftimes the national average.
OL,13,FThe proposal follows the Government's
OL,14,FEnglish Devolution White Paper, which
OL,15,Frequires every local authority area to
OL,16,Fbe part of a strategic authority. The
OL,17,FGovernment has confirmed that the West
OL,18,Fof England is 'the best fit' for North
OL,19,FSomerset and has asked the region to
OL,20,Fseek views before any decision is
OL,21,Ftaken.
