OL,3,CShould North Somerset join the
OL,4,Ccombined authority? Consultation gets
OL,5,Cunderway
OL,7,FReacting to the news, Helen Godwin,
OL,8,FMayor of the West of England, said:
OL,9,F"Together we have negotiated a deal
OL,10,Fthat's a real vote of confidence from
OL,11,Fthe Government. The new chapter that
OL,12,Fwe have started in the West is being
OL,13,Fbacked up with new investment."
OL,15,FMayor Godwin continued: "Millions of
OL,16,Fpounds more for local projects, and a
OL,17,Fcommitment to greater funding in
OL,18,Ffuture based on our larger geography,
OL,19,Fwould make a real difference for
OL,20,Fcommunities across our region."
