OL,3,CShould North Somerset join the
OL,4,Ccombined authority? Consultation gets
OL,5,Cunderway
OL,7,FMeanwhile, Councillor Mike Bell,
OL,8,FLeader of North Somerset Council,
OL,9,Fsaid: "I hope that people across the
OL,10,Farea will get involved in the
OL,11,Fconsultation and share their views."
OL,13,FHe added: "This is a pivotal point for
OL,14,FNorth Somerset which will enable us to
OL,15,Fensure that our local communities get
OL,16,Fmaximum benefit from powers ` and
OL,17,Ffunding ` being devolved from central
OL,18,Fgovernment.
