OL,3,CShould North Somerset join the
OL,4,Ccombined authority? Consultation gets
OL,5,Cunderway
OL,7,F"Our region is stronger when working
OL,8,Ftogether and I hope the expansion will
OL,9,Fbe supported so we can deliver lasting
OL,10,Fimprovements for everyone across the
OL,11,FWest."
OL,13,FIf approved, and subject to the
OL,14,Fparliamentary calendar, the
OL,15,Flegislative process would be expected
OL,16,Fto take around eight weeks, with North
OL,17,FSomerset able to become a full member
OL,18,Fof the West of England Mayoral
OL,19,FCombined Authority from late 2026 or
OL,20,Fearly 2027.
