OL,3,CShould North Somerset join the
OL,4,Ccombined authority? Consultation gets
OL,5,Cunderway
OL,7,FThe next election of the Mayor of the
OL,8,FWest of England would take place in
OL,9,FMay 2029.
OL,11,FAn expansion of the combined authority
OL,12,Fwould also support its efforts to
OL,13,Fbecome an Established Mayoral
OL,14,FStrategic Authority (EMSA), like West
OL,15,FYorkshire and Greater Manchester.
OL,17,FThat would allow budgets to be fully
OL,18,Fdevolved from Westminster for housing,
OL,19,Fregeneration, local growth, local
OL,20,Ftransport, skills, retrofit, and
OL,21,Femployment support.
